<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
html { background: #ffffff; }
body {
  width: 720pt; height: 405pt; margin: 0; padding: 0;
  background: #ffffff;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.header {
  width: 720pt;
  height: 40pt;
  background: #181B24;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding-left: 20pt;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.header h1 {
  color: #B165FB;
  font-size: 22pt;
  margin: 0;
}
.content {
  width: 720pt;
  height: 365pt;
  padding: 12pt 20pt;
  display: flex;
  gap: 12pt;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.left-col {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10pt;
}
.right-col {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10pt;
}
.paper-box {
  background: #B165FB;
  padding: 12pt;
  border-radius: 6pt;
  color: #ffffff;
  flex: 1;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.paper-box h2 {
  font-size: 16pt;
  margin: 0 0 8pt 0;
  
  padding-bottom: 5pt;
}
.paper-box p {
  font-size: 12pt;
  margin: 5px 0;
}
.innovation-box {
  background: #f8f9fa;
  padding: 10pt;
  border-radius: 6pt;
  border-left: 4pt solid #40695B;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.innovation-box h2 {
  color: #181B24;
  font-size: 16pt;
  margin: 0 0 8pt 0;
}
.innovation-box ul {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 16pt;
  color: #40695B;
}
.innovation-box li {
  font-size: 11pt;
  margin-bottom: 5pt;
}
.impact-box {
  background: #e7f3ff;
  padding: 10pt;
  border-radius: 6pt;
  border-left: 4pt solid #B165FB;
  flex: 1;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.impact-box h2 {
  color: #181B24;
  font-size: 16pt;
  margin: 0 0 8pt 0;
}
.impact-box ul {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 16pt;
  color: #181B24;
}
.impact-box li {
  font-size: 11pt;
  margin-bottom: 5pt;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
  <h1>Transformer - 架构革命</h1>
</div>
<div class="content">
  <div class="left-col">
    <div class="paper-box">
      <h2>论文</h2>
      <p><strong>"Attention Is All You Need"</strong></p>
      <p><strong>2017</strong></p>
      <p>Vaswani et al. (Google)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="innovation-box">
      <h2>核心创新</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>自注意力机制：</strong>捕捉序列依赖</li>
        <li><strong>并行计算：</strong>比 RNN 快</li>
        <li><strong>编码器-解码器</strong></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="right-col">
    <div class="impact-box">
      <h2>影响</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>NLP 提升（翻译、摘要、问答）</li>
        <li>计算机视觉（ViT）</li>
        <li>多模态（CLIP, DALL-E）</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
